	// providers{{end}}), a
	// pack took over (middleware.MarkExternalAuth), the operator typed
	// the explicit opt-out (AUTH_MODE=none), or auth is explicitly
	// bypassed for dev. The passthrough is gated on cfg.DevAuthBypass()
